            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>green beans </strong>to a pot with a pinch of salt and cover with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 7,
